---

<Base title="12 Best English Podcasts for Beginners in 2026" description="From absolute beginner to confident intermediate, these 12 podcasts will train your ear, grow your vocabulary, and build a daily habit that actually works.">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(articleSchema)} />
  
  <Header />
  
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
